      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive</strong> <strong>oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>shallot</strong> <strong>wedges</strong> and <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>carrot</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
      "order": 3,
