    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the veg is softening, dissolve your <strong>beef</strong> <strong>stock</strong> <strong>mix</strong>, <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>paste</strong> and <strong>red</strong> <strong>wine</strong> <strong>paste</strong> in 250ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[320ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[420ml]</span> <strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water</strong> – this is your <strong>red wine stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
