    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the carrot and onion has slightly softened, add your <strong>beef</strong> <strong>mince</strong> to the pan with your <strong>bay leaf[ves]</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to brown, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p><p>Once browned, reduce the heat to medium-high, add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> and 1/2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3/4 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong> and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
