    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>red wine stock</strong> with a grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 4-5 min or until the sauce has thickened and the beef is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>beef & red wine stew</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
