    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the<strong> cooked potatoes</strong> to a low heat with a small knob of <strong>butter</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>horseradish</strong> <strong>sauce</strong> (not a big horseradish fan? Try using less!)<strong> </strong>and mash until smooth – this is your <strong>horseradish mash</strong></p>",
