      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>beef & red wine stew</strong> over the <strong>horseradish</strong> <strong>mash</strong>, discard the <strong>bay leaf[ves]</strong></p><p>Season with a grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>and garnish with the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>parsley</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
